					Latest Key Developments (Source: Significant Developments)




Yamada Consulting Group to establish investment limited liability partnership
Tuesday, 18 Jul 2017 
July 18 (Reuters) - Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:* Says it plans to establish an investment limited liability partnership with Japan Post Bank Co Ltd <7182.T>, Toho Bank Ltd <8346.T>, and Fukushima-based unit of Toho Bank Ltd, on Aug. 1 .* Says investment amount of 500 million yen in total. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group consolidated subsidiary announces business and capital alliance with Bexuco
Friday, 16 Jun 2017 
June 16(Reuters) - Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:Says its consolidated subsidiary YAMADA Business Consulting Co.,Ltd acquired a part of shares of Bexuco Limited on June 8.Says YAMADA Business Consulting announces business alliance with Bexuco and Bexuco's wholly owned Shanghai-based unit BEXUCO (Shanghai) Investment Consulting Co.,Ltd., regarding cross-border M&A business . 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group consolidated subsidiary to set up unit YBC Capital in Thailand
Friday, 16 Jun 2017 
June 16(Reuters) - Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:Says its consolidated subsidiary YAMADA Business Consulting Co.,Ltd will set up a Thailand-based new unit YBC Capital Co.,Ltd., which will be mainly engaged in investment business, on June 30.Says this new unit will be capitalized at 2 million baht (about 6 million yen). 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group announces merger between wholly owed units
Thursday, 18 May 2017 
May 18(Reuters) - Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:Says it plans merger between two Tokyo-based wholly owned units, YAMADA Business Consulting Co Ltd and YAMADA FAS Co Ltd.Merger effective date on July 1.Says YAMADA FAS will be dissolved after the transaction. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group unit forms business alliance with Takenaka Partners LLC
Tuesday, 20 Dec 2016 
Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:Says its business consulting unit entered into agreement with the U.S.-based firm Takenaka Partners LLC to form alliance on overseas business. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group unit forms business alliance with Toyo Business Service Public Co Ltd
Tuesday, 20 Dec 2016 
Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd <4792.T>:Says its business consulting unit entered into agreement with Thailand-based firm Toyo Business Service Public Company Limited to form business alliance at Thailand market. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group to issue year-end dividend for FY 2016
Wednesday, 27 Apr 2016 
Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd:To issue a year-end dividend of 60 yen per share to all the shareholders of record as of March 31, for FY ended March 2016.Payment date June 2.Says latest dividend forecast was 55 yen per share. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group completes 80 pct stake acquisition in SPIRE Research and Consulting Pte Ltd
Friday, 15 Apr 2016 
Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd:Completes 80 pct stake acquisition in SPIRE Research and Consulting Pte Ltd on April 15.Plan was disclosed on March 14. 
			
Full Article





Yamada Consulting Group to buy 80 pct stake in SPIRE Research and Consulting Pte Ltd
Monday, 14 Mar 2016 
Yamada Consulting Group Co Ltd:To buy a 160,000 shares in SPIRE Research and Consulting Pte Ltd from an individual Leon Perera in mid-April at an undisclosed price.To raise stake in SPIRE Research and Consulting Pte Ltd to 80 pct from 0 pct after the transaction. 
			
