Company Overview of YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. provides various consulting services in Japan and internationally. It offers management consulting services, such as sustained growth, business revitalization and succession, and M and A consulting services; real estate consulting services; financial advisory services on capital, stocks, and shareholders; and financial planners related and insurance agency services, as well as establishes and manages business succession fund to support business succession of middle and small businesses. The company was formerly known as TFP Consulting Group Co., Ltd. and changed its name to YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. in December 2010. YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd....
YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. provides various consulting services in Japan and internationally. It offers management consulting services, such as sustained growth, business revitalization and succession, and M and A consulting services; real estate consulting services; financial advisory services on capital, stocks, and shareholders; and financial planners related and insurance agency services, as well as establishes and manages business succession fund to support business succession of middle and small businesses. The company was formerly known as TFP Consulting Group Co., Ltd. and changed its name to YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. in December 2010. YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 1989 and is based in Tokyo, Japan.
