Business summary
YAMADA Consulting Group Co., Ltd. engages in the provision of financial consulting services. It operates through the following business segments: Business Consulting, Capital, Stocks, and Shareholder-Related Consulting, Real Estate Consulting, Financial Planner Consulting, and Investment Fund Consulting. The Business Consulting segment includes business revival, operations, and financial consulting. The Capital, Stocks, and Shareholder-Related Consulting segment includes stock listing consulting, mergers and acquisitions advisory and valuation business. The Real Estate Consulting segment includes real estate consulting and brokerage. The Financial Planner Consulting segment includes marketing course, corporate training, and insurance consulting for financial planners. The Investment Fund Consulting segment includes composition and management of investment partnership and investment business. The company was founded on July 10, 1989 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.







